flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 63A: Vendor Operations Business-Friendly Journey

  Join[Vendor joins and submits KYC documents]
  Approve[Verification approved and dashboard unlocked]
  Plan[Vendor selects subscription and feature plan]
  Sell[Vendor publishes products and runs campaigns]
  Stock[AI guidance supports inventory and reorder timing]
  Finance[Escrow release, payout, and reconciliation complete]
  Learn[Academy progress unlocks badges and growth milestones]

  Issue{Any issue appears?}
  Resolve[Support, compliance, or finance resolves the issue]
  Growth[Vendor growth continues]

  Join --> Approve --> Plan --> Sell --> Stock --> Finance --> Learn --> Issue
  Issue -- No --> Growth
  Issue -- Yes --> Resolve --> Growth
